comments.content: I looked at the review but still think this issue needs to b e addressed. The point of this ticket, and the other tickets about ERRORs in the logs, is that we want to be able to fail gating tests  and allow operators to alert if there are ERRORs in the logs. It is not necessary to remove the information from the log, but the message should be changed to DEBUG if it is there for debugging reasons.
